/** * Gets the least supertype of {@code this} and {@code that}. * The least supertype is the join (∨) or supremum of both types in the * type lattice.

* Examples: *

    *
  • {@code number ∨ *} = {@code *}
    • *
  • {@code number ∨ Object} = {@code (number, Object)}
    • *
  • {@code Number ∨ Object} = {@code Object}
    • *
* @return {@code this ∨ that} */
